casebody.data:
No. 1112,

October Term, 1968.

Leighton v. One William Street Fund, Inc., et al.,

394 U. S. 988, 395 U. S. 942. Motion for relief pendente'lite denied.

Mr. Justice Marshall took no part in the consideration or decision of this motion. Motion for leave to file second petition for rehearing denied. The Chief Justice, Mr. Justice Marshall, and Mr. Justice Blackmun took no part in the consideration or decision of the latter motion.
